From 105aca36ada9daf1ec2fea88d1ca904ea6a21ec5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: MEHAAT <dev@mehaat.local>
Date: Sat, 18 Jul 2026 09:42:40 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] v10.2: Real-time WhatsApp Support Console with manual live
 reply

Additive upgrade to the admin dashboard: live inbox, WhatsApp-style live chat,
manual reply (text/image/pdf/voice via Meta media upload), per-conversation
AI/Manual toggle that gates the bot's auto-reply, conversation assignment,
admin-only internal notes, message delivery/read status, customer profile,
Shopify product-card/draft-order, payment-link generation, live stats, browser+
sound notifications. Polling-based real-time (3s), WhatsApp-Business UI with
dark/light. New tables via Alembic (conversation_settings, admin_messages,
conversation_assignments, internal_notes, message_status). No existing feature,
route, table or API changed. 361 tests pass; verified on SQLite and PostgreSQL.
